{"tid":2355679,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周浩鼎斥612基金支援「黑暴」 葛珮帆：國安法實施後應調查眾籌活動","createTime":"2021-01-06T09:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T12:12:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ada70ef70df0b0e8a24f6d2c908e0ef13d213f1c","tid":2355679,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）民建聯周浩鼎於立法會提出質詢，質疑「612人道支援基金」是否合法運作。保安局局長李家超回應指，利用所有法律手段打擊任何人籌款作不法用途，是「首要行動策略」。民建聯葛珮帆指，前年6月至今有多個組織借助眾籌和基金平台支援「黑暴」及港獨份子，政府在《國安法》實施後，「應主動出擊調查眾籌活動，而唔係等人舉報」。<br />\n<br />\n李家超：打擊資金被非法利用為首要行動策略<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎提出的質詢問及，政府有否監察612人道支援基金是否合法運作、會否立法規管網上籌款活動，及會否取消向已獲612人道支援基金資助聘用法律代表的被告提供法援。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超表示，網上眾籌的金錢運用必須合法，政府會持續監察，如違法必處理，又強調資金可令人有規模、組織地行事，以法律打擊資金被非法利用乃政府首要行動策略。<br />\n<br />\n李家超續指，現時有足夠的法律打擊相關違法行為，包括洗黑錢罪、欺詐罪以及《國安法》，其中資助他人實施違反《國安法》的罪行，最高可判處無期徒刑，而《國安法》亦賦予執法部門權力凍結違法資金。<br />\n<br />\n李家超亦引法援署回覆指，批出法援的準則為案件是否有合理抗辯理由及申請人的經濟背景，過往有少數人會因案件複雜程度被資助第二名大律師，而年輕大律師只收車馬費甚至義務參與案件以累積經驗，亦是法律界「行之已久」的方法，不會出現雙重支援的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎籲政府「緊盯612基金，一有違法行為就拉人封艇」。他續批法援署的回覆是「卸膊」和「不對焦」，斥既然基金開宗明義支援「黑暴」找法律代表，「點解法律援助仲要批錢？」李家超僅指有責任確保公帑如何善用，會轉達相關意見。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080037&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImevO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=48378305\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080037&h=ed4479e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080037</a>"},{"pid":"ac5b338698d094276b601a81d6fef2b6629f340e","tid":2355679,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bd19d616c50651694aebcf4c94b87c1a8f2e04","tid":2355679,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩隻忠犬"},{"pid":"ff77a81a594f4c86f305f7b0c7b40bb08131a8c9","tid":2355679,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f223c8f34912c68c2c24086c187219c258d21ba6","tid":2355679,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T11:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a08e639753c4b9b838670cfdef5e997ee859791","tid":2355679,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:11:07.000Z","msg":"得啦，知你民建聯專門支援&ldquo;情操高尚&rdquo;既鄉黑，唔洗查都知你地source of funds就係支那共匪"},{"pid":"b253cb516432ad39e4b953511e7bf18767b2e4ce","tid":2355679,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38bd19d616c50651694aebcf4c94b87c1a8f2e04","tid":2355679,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T09:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩隻忠犬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"唔做狗邊有利用價值"}]}